metadata.name: Ariel The Bloodthirsty Angel
metadata.description:
**Sanctuary for The Misfits: 1**

As an angel from the powers hierarchy, Ariel is doomed to fight and spill the enemy's blood for eternity.

Which, she will gladly do - and takes gratification from it.

.....Until she got cast out and hunted down by her kin for slaying someone she shouldn't.

After all, an angel is supposed to be obedient and stick to the rules given.
